messages.subject: Recipe Swap
messages.msgSnippet: Okay guys, I have created an unschooling recipes group at yahoo groups.  I left it private, so only those of you who get this on the unschooling list will know
messages.messageBody:
Okay guys,
I have created an unschooling recipes group at yahoo groups. I left it
private, so only those of you who get this on the unschooling list will
know about it, but feel free to pass it on to other homeschoolers you
think might enjoy it!!
Lets swap those recipes!
Ann
You can go here to join....
http://groups.yahoo.com/group/unschoolingrecipes

or send a subscribe message here....

unschoolingrecipes-subscribe@yahoogroups.com
